title: The One After Joey and Rachel Kiss
synopsis: Ross has kissed Charlie although she is still officially dating Joey. Joey and Rachel have kissed as well, but they agonize over how to tell Ross.

title: The One Where Ross Is Fine
synopsis: Rachel, Joey and Charlie attend an uncomfortable dinner party at Ross's apartment. Former surrogate mother Phoebe is visited by her brother, Frank Jr.

title: The One with Ross's Tan
synopsis: Monica and Phoebe's annoying friend visits, causing a rift between the women. Ross goes to a tanning salon but fails to follow the directions.

title: The One with the Cake
synopsis: When Ross dashes out to help Rachel for Emma's birthday party, he leaves Joey in charge of keeping everybody in the apartment until they return.

title: The One Where Rachel's Sister Babysits
synopsis: Rachel thinks her annoying, self-indulgent younger sister, Amy, is finally on the verge of making a major change in her attitude.

title: The One with Ross's Grant
synopsis: Ross has the chance to receive a grant, but must break up with Charlie to get it. Phoebe tries to give a hideous painting to Monica and Rachel.

title: The One with The Home Study
synopsis: Phoebe and Mike opt to have a small wedding and donate the extra money to a children's charity -- only to demand it all back later.

title: The One with the Late Thanksgiving
synopsis: Monica prepares a fabulous Thanksgiving feast for the gang, but she becomes furious when everyone arrives late to the gathering.

title: The One with the Birth Mother
synopsis: Nervous and excited, Monica and Chandler travel to Ohio to meet a pregnant woman who is considering allowing them to adopt her child when it's born.

title: The One Where Chandler Gets Caught
synopsis: When Phoebe and Rachel see Chandler getting into a car with a pretty woman during work hours, they follow him.

title: The One Where the Stripper Cries
synopsis: Joey appears as a celebrity contestant on "The $100,000 Pyramid," but his dubious IQ puts his partner's prize money at risk.

title: The One with Phoebe's Wedding
synopsis: Phoebe's wedding planner, Monica, is driving everyone around her crazy. Chandler and Ross lobby Rachel to choose one of them as a groomsman.

title: The One Where Joey Speaks French
synopsis: Monica and Chandler show Erica, the mother of the unborn baby they want to adopt, the sights of New York. Joey implores Phoebe to teach him French.

title: The One with Princess Consuela
synopsis: Rachel nearly gags on her meal when she goes on a job interview at a restaurant and sits next to her current boss. Phoebe considers changing her name.

title: The One Where Estelle Dies
synopsis: When Rachel makes a startling announcement, Ross schemes to get her former job back for her. Joey is flustered by the upheaval in his friends' lives.

title: The One with Rachel's Going Away Party
synopsis: As Rachel prepares to leave for Paris, the gang hosts a farewell party for her. But one friend is offended when he is excluded.

title: The Last One: Part 1 & Part 2
synopsis: On their last day together, Rachel, Monica, Phoebe, Joey, Chandler and Ross reflect on their shared times with bittersweet emotion.
